Package: httrex
Type: Package
Title: Create code examples that include http requests
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person(
            given = "Greg",
            family = "Freedman Ellis",
            email = "greg.freedman@gmail.com",
            role = c("aut", "cre")
        )
    )
Description: Convenience wrapper for 'reprex'-like creation of code snippets
    that specializes in displaying the http requests made by R functions
    so that authors of R 'API' clients can communicate with the authors of 
    'API' providers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
